<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>2026 버킷리스트 </title>
    <style>
        .card {
            width: 320px;
            border: 2px solid #333;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 5px 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            
    
            position: relative; 
            margin: 50px auto;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .card img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .badge {
            position: absolute; 
            top: -10px;         
            right: -10px;        
            background-color: #ffcc00;
            color: #000;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 50px;
            border: 2px solid #000;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        
        .secret-memo {
            visibility: hidden; 
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            border: 1px dashed #aaa;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-top: 15px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #555;
        }

        
        .card:hover .secret-memo {
            visibility: visible; 
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="card">
        <div class="badge">2026</div>
        
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507525428034-b723cf961d3e?w=500&auto=format&fit=crop&q=60" alt="바다 풍경">
        
        <h2> 이서호 버킷리스트</h2>
        
        <div style="text-align: left; display: inline-block;">
            <p> 1. 혼자 여행가보기</p>
            <p> 2. 웹사이트 만들어서 배포해보기</p>
            <p> 3. 자격증 취득</p> 
        </div>
        
        <div class="secret-memo">
            TMI: 오버워치 좋아합니다!
        </div>
    </div>
    </body>
</html>
